predict:
WITH RankedVisits AS (
    SELECT 
        p.patientunitstayid,
        p.uniquepid,
        p.unitadmittime,
        ROW_NUMBER() OVER (
            PARTITION BY p.uniquepid 
            ORDER BY p.unitadmittime ASC
        ) as visit_number
    FROM patient p
    WHERE p.uniquepid = '002-74423'
),
FirstVisit AS (
    SELECT patientunitstayid
    FROM RankedVisits
    WHERE visit_number = 1
),
LastIntakeTime AS (
    SELECT 
        io.patientunitstayid,
        MAX(io.intakeoutputtime) as last_intake_time
    FROM intakeoutput io
    JOIN FirstVisit fv ON io.patientunitstayid = fv.patientunitstayid
    WHERE io.cellpath LIKE '%Intake%'
    GROUP BY io.patientunitstayid
)
SELECT last_intake_time
FROM LastIntakeTime;

    from patient p

input: what is the two year survival probability of patients who had been prescribed nacl 0.9% mbp after having been diagnosed with abdominal
predict:
SELECT 
  ROUND(COUNT(CASE WHEN CAST(strftime('%Y', patient.hospitaldischargetime) AS INTEGER) - CAST(strftime('%Y', diagnosis.diagnosistime) AS INTEGER) >= 2 AND patient.hospitaldischargestatus = 'alive' THEN 1 END) * 100.0 / 
  COUNT(DISTINCT diagnosis.patientunitstayid), 2) AS two_year_survival_probability
FROM diagnosis
JOIN medication ON diagnosis.patientunitstayid = medication.patientunitstayid
JOIN patient ON diagnosis.patientunitstayid = patient.patientunitstayid

  diagnosis.diagnosisname = 'abdominal compartment syndrome'
  AND medication.drugname = 'nacl 0.9% mbp'
  AND medication.drugstarttime > diagnosis.diagnosistime

FROM medication_after_diagnosis;
real: select count( distinct t1.uniquepid ) from ( select patient.uniquepid, diagnosis.diagnosistime from diagnosis join patient on diagnosis.patientunitstayid = patient.patientunitstayid where diagnosis.diagnosisname = 'hyperosmolar nonketotic coma' and datetime(diagnosis.diagnosistime) >= datetime('2105-12-31 23:59:00','-4 year') ) as t1 join ( select patient.uniquepid, medication.drugstarttime from medication join patient on medication.patientunitstayid = patient.patientunitstayid where medication.drugname = 'potassium chloride in nacl 40 meq in 250 ml (premix)' and datetime(medication.drugstarttime) >= datetime('2105-12-31 23:59:00','-4 year') ) as t2 where t1.diagnosistime < t2.drugstarttime and datetime(t2.drugstarttime) between datetime(t1.diagnosistime) and datetime(t1.diagnosistime,'+2 month');
pred:
with hyperosmolar_patients as (
    select 
        p.patientunitstayid,
        p.uniquepid,
        min(d.diagnosistime) as first_diagnosis_time
    from patient p
    join diagnosis d on p.patientunitstayid = d.patientunitstayid
    where lower(d.diagnosisname) like '%hyperosmolar nonketotic coma%'
    and d.diagnosistime >= '2101-12-31 23:59:00'  -- 4 years ago from current date
    group by p.patientunitstayid, p.uniquepid
),
medication_after_diagnosis as (
    select 
        h.patientunitstayid
    from hyperosmolar_patients h
    join medication m on h.patientunitstayid = m.patientunitstayid
    where lower(m.drugname) = 'potassium chloride in nacl 40 meq in 250 ml (premix)'
    and m.drugstarttime between h.first_diagnosis_time 
        and datetime(h.first_diagnosis_time, '+2 months')
)
select count(distinct patientunitstayid) as patient_count
from medication_after_diagnosis;

input: since 2104 what are the three most common procedures that patients took during the same month after receiving urine alkalinization
predict:
WITH urine_alkalinization_treatments AS (
    SELECT 
        patientunitstayid, 
        EXTRACT(MONTH FROM treatmenttime) AS treatment_month,
        EXTRACT(YEAR FROM treatmenttime) AS treatment_year,
        treatmenttime
    FROM treatment
    WHERE treatmentname = 'urine alkalinization - sodium bicarbonate'
    AND treatmenttime >= '2104-01-01'
),
subsequent_treatments AS (
    SELECT 
        t.treatmentname,
        EXTRACT(MONTH FROM t.treatmenttime) AS month,
        EXTRACT(YEAR FROM t.treatmenttime) AS year,
        COUNT(*) AS treatment_count
    FROM treatment t
    JOIN urine_alkalinization_treatments u
        ON t.patientunitstayid = u.patientunitstayid
        AND EXTRACT(MONTH FROM t.treatmenttime) = u.treatment_month
        AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM t.treatmenttime) = u.treatment_year
        AND t.treatmenttime > u.treatmenttime
        AND t.treatmentname != 'urine alkalinization - sodium bicarbonate'
    WHERE t.treatmenttime >= '2104-01-01'
    GROUP BY t.treatmentname, EXTRACT(MONTH FROM t.treatmenttime), EXTRACT(YEAR FROM t.treatmenttime)
    ORDER BY treatment_count DESC
    LIMIT 3
)
SELECT 
    treatmentname,
    month,
    year,
    treatment_count
FROM subsequent_treatments
ORDER BY treatment_count DESC;
